Everybody was taken by the aliens, man. It had to be the aliens."There's no such thing as aliens.

00:19:48.880 --> 00:19:55.918
I'm telling you, it's demonic spirits—Nephilim, whatever you want to say.

00:19:55.919 --> 00:20:03.199
