00:20:19.092 --> 00:20:26.475
It's not like that. I'm talking about it looks huge. It's like 13 feet high—a massive being.

00:20:26.476 --> 00:20:31.314
It's some kind of thing. I've seen visions of it. How many times now, son?

00:20:31.315 --> 00:20:35.105
So many. Looked like a log creature. It's the way the skin looks.

00:20:35.106 --> 00:20:44.239
It comes out and starts talking to people and then there's a mothership that will appear over the Vatican. I've seen it.

