00:21:09.786 --> 00:21:14.408
There's a lot of people who get mad and say, "I don't believe in the rapture of the church."That's fine.

00:21:14.409 --> 00:21:23.599
Stay here. I'll wave at you as I'm going up. But I'm telling you, we're not appointed unto wrath.

00:21:23.600 --> 00:21:30.399
We're not appointed unto wrath. God is not a wife-beater. He's not going to beat his bride.

00:21:30.400 --> 00:21:34.420
You say, "Well, Brandon, the disciples went through a lot."Yes, they did.

00:21:34.421 --> 00:21:41.914
