00:23:37.280 --> 00:23:47.452
These people are sick. But the next one—I've told you a hundred times.

00:23:47.453 --> 00:23:51.402
If you get the virus, you do not make it unless you have the glory.

00:23:51.403 --> 00:23:57.343
I saw the people. They were hiding. They had barricades around the house.

00:23:57.344 --> 00:24:02.234
"Don't come. Stay away."We got our own food. You come next to us, you're gone.

00:24:02.235 --> 00:24:07.249
People acted crazy. You think it was bad to covet what people wanted?

00:24:07.250 --> 00:24:14.606
Toilet paper. People want food this time. Factories were shut down.

00:24:14.607 --> 00:24:31.471
