Understand covenant. Whenever you put that ring on your finger and I say "I do"to my wife, I will be married to her until the day I die.

00:25:10.483 --> 00:25:25.678
This is a covenant. This represents the covenant. She has a ring on her finger. I'm in covenant with God. As He is, so am I in this world.

00:25:25.679 --> 00:25:35.439
And if we pray and we know the signs of the times—because Jesus told us in Matthew 24 that these things were coming—we're not afraid.

00:25:35.440 --> 00:25:47.359
Why? Because the Bible already told us it was coming. What are we to do? Get ready for the harvest. Where is the scripture?

00:25:47.360 --> 00:25:56.552
"Be patient."In James 5:7: "Be patient, therefore, brethren, until the coming of the Lord.

00:25:56.553 --> 00:26:18.158
Behold, the husbandman waiteth for the precious fruit of the earth and hath long patience for it until he receives the early and the latter rain."James 5:7.

00:26:18.159 --> 00:26:26.479
So what are we waiting for right now? The Lord said specifically to me, "You're not waiting on me; I'm waiting on you.

